latestIgtvVideos.title: Be You💫
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
They will want you to be in your best behaviour ... be graceful and put up smile in a perfect curve.

But dear women they say it all because they are scared of your wilderness, 
Because they are scared to evolve into their own self.
So go ahead ...
Dance barefoot, laugh it out, embrace your rawness and be as crazy as you can.
Be You.

And as you transcend into this Supersoul that you are always meant to be ... Nothing else will matter.

🐾 Small Acts, Big Impact! 🐦💧

As @lavinatandon05 says, “A little care goes a long way!"

Ever thought about how a simple bowl of water can quench a bird’s thirst in the scorching heat? 
Or how a small corner of shelter can protect a stray from heavy rains? 🌧️ 
And in winter, an old blanket left outside can be a lifesaver for animals seeking warmth. ❄️

Before starting your car, take a moment to check underneath—because sometimes, a life may be waiting there. 🚗❤️

It’s not about big actions, but small, thoughtful gestures that make a world of difference.
